See `src/app/api/queues/persist-media-to-r2/__tests__/persist-media-to-r2.test.ts`
for an example of a Route Handler test in this codebase.

### Notes

- Co-locate tests in a sibling `__tests__` directory or alongside the route
  as `route.test.ts`.
- Use `createTestRequest()` (or `new Request(...)`) to build request objects.
- Mock `global.fetch` for all external API calls.
- Verify both HTTP status codes and the custom envelope `code`.
- Use `as unknown as Response` for mock Response objects to avoid TS errors.
